      "summary": "Vlad Ionescu (he/him) jokingly describes himself as a “Professional mistake avoider”, which he argues is a better way of saying “Independent Consultant”. His work is devoted to getting companies to high-performing levels. Vlad swings wildly on the engineer/manager pendulum, and he is always full of energy. As an Individual Contributor, he focuses on architecting resilient applications and on growing engineers. As a Manager, he focuses on empowering people to do their best work and on building sustainable companies. In parallel to his tech career, Vlad is a foodie and very much into cocktails, whiskey, and wine — finding him at a tasting or food pairing event is a sure bet. He cherishes mental health and is an avid proponent of any effort in the area.",
